Different figures of merit are used commonly to characterize the sensing performance of the photodetectors, including responsivity (Rλ), external quantum efficiency (EQE), and detectivity (D). These parameters are described by the following equations92,935Rλ=IPCPopt=IPCIL·S,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
